{"tid":902372,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"想推介一套漫畫《星野，閉上眼》","createTime":"2018-11-14T18:19:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T08:11:02.000Z","uid":87132,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"071eff6b928ece759172925c2c5b510873086f27","tid":902372,"uid":87132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T18:19:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/ELTN14n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FELTN14n.jpg&h=fbc7682d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而套漫畫係戀愛類型，但比其他唔同嘅地方係男主嘅性格較為陰沉，一直被班上同學無視<br />\n隨住劇情發展，男主需要幫女主每日化妝，而同時想慢慢改變自己<br />\n<br />\n而我較喜歡男主會唔理他人目光，去捍衛自己認為嘅正確。亦因如此，慢慢有各式各樣嘅人找男主麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n暫時更新到66集更加係故事嘅高潮，令我忍唔住向各位巴打推介<br />\n希望大家中意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n漫畫link: （求其搵嘅漫畫網）<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.manhuagui.com/comic/20017\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.manhuagui.com%2Fcomic%2F20017&d=o6syI3ret%2BUysVreybH4RU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=e4b7e4c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.manhuagui.com/comic/20017</a>/"},{"pid":"89b359de3b0c489ff2de65229392f00d2ac23a3c","tid":902372,"uid":106701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T18:27:39.000Z","msg":"初初有追，但之後變咗男主周圍幫人就冇睇"},{"pid":"4a7e2f271d1edeeeed9f966ca4584cdd3b8e3524","tid":902372,"uid":82404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89b359de3b0c489ff2de65229392f00d2ac23a3c","tid":902372,"uid":106701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T18:27:39.000Z","msg":"初初有追，但之後變咗男主周圍幫人就冇睇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T18:38:35.000Z","msg":"+1<br />\n追追下冇咩動力睇"},{"pid":"41fe4c0e7c8952b814705aba9653bb6fbb35ecc6","tid":902372,"uid":87132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a7e2f2